    "created_at": "2015-03-27T03:15:00Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-03-27T03:15:00Z",
    "body": "Possible solutions are to either remove the impl for `&mut [u8]` or update `write!` to prevent it from invoking `DerefMut`. Seems to me like the second is the better approach.\n",
